in any geographic<A NAME = "AB1792127"></A><A HREF = "SPP81.HTM#BB1837127"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> area in which the video<A NAME = "BB1792138"></A><A HREF = "SPP80.HTM#BB180978"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> programming services offered by
the operator in that area are subject to effective competition, or (2) any
