<A NAME = "AE14830"></A><A NAME = "AE14830"></A><A HREF = "SPP184.HTM#AO421743"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Telecommunications carrier that receives or obtains customer proprietary network information by virtue of provision of telecommunications service only use, disclose or permit access to individually identifiable customer proprietary network information in provision <P>
<A HREF = "SPP184.HTM#AO4217135"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Telecommunications service from which information being derived or services necessary to provision of telecommunications service including publishing of directories <P>
<A HREF = "SPP184.HTM#AO42196"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>DISCLOSURE on REQUEST by CUSTOMERS-A telecommunications carrier to disclose customer proprietary network information to person designated by customer <P>
