<A HREF = "SPP184.HTM#AO4221106"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Local exchange carrier to use, disclose or permit access to aggregate customer information other than purposes described in paragraph only if provides aggregate information to other carriers or persons on reasonable and nondiscriminatory terms and conditions upon reasonable request therefor <P>
<A NAME = "AE14880"></A><A HREF = "SPP184.HTM#AO42236"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>EXCEPTIONS-Nothing in section prohibits telecommunications carrier from using, disclosing or permitting access to customer proprietary network information obtained from customers <P>
<A NAME = "AE14890"></A><A HREF = "SPP185.HTM#AO422916"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Referral or administrative services to customer for duration of call if call initiated by customer and customer approves of use of information to provide service <P>
<A HREF = "SPP185.HTM#AO423134"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Telecommunications carrier that provides telephone exchange service to provide subscriber list information gathered in capacity as provider of service <P>
