in, or uses a facility or means of,';
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>(2) by inserting `or an interactive computer service (as defined
in section 230(e)(2) of the Communications Act of 1934) in or affecting such
commerce' after `foreign commerce' the first place it appears;
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>(3) by striking<A NAME = "AO34907"></A> `, or knowingly travels in' and all that follows
through `obscene material in interstate or foreign commerce,' and inserting
`of'.
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><P>
