this Act;
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>`(2) such sums as may be appropriated to the Commission for advances
to the Fund;
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>`(3) any contributions<A NAME = "AO45918"></A> or donations to the Fund that are accepted
by the Fund; and
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>`(4) any repayment of, or other payment made with respect to,
loans<A NAME = "AO459327"></A>, equity, or other extensions of credit made from the Fund.
