person or persons under 18 years of age, or
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(B) uses<A NAME = "AO30386"></A><A NAME = "AS30387"></A> any interactive<A NAME = "BB303812"></A><A HREF = "SPP157.HTM#BB357735"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> computer service to display in a
