as measured by contemporary community standards, sexual or excretory<A NAME = "BB304057"></A><A HREF = "SPAP1.HTM#AF283557"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> activities
or organs, regardless<A NAME = "AO304066"></A> of whether the user of such service placed the call
or initiated the communication; or
</UL></UL><P>
