<A HREF = "SPP186.HTM#AO4257106"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Local exchange carrier to use, disclose or permit access to aggregate customer information other than purposes described in paragraph only if provides aggregate information to other carriers or persons on reasonable and nondiscriminatory terms and conditions upon reasonable request therefor <P>
<A HREF = "SPP186.HTM#AO42596"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>EXCEPTIONS-Nothing in section prohibits telecommunications carrier from using, disclosing or permitting access to customer proprietary network information obtained from customers <P>
<A HREF = "SPP186.HTM#AO426516"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Referral or administrative services to customer for duration of call if call initiated by customer and customer approves of use of information to provide service <P>
<A HREF = "SPP187.HTM#AO426734"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Telecommunications carrier that provides telephone exchange service to provide subscriber list information gathered in capacity as provider of service <P>
<A NAME = "AE15040"></A><A NAME = "AE15040"></A><A NAME = "AE15040"></A><A HREF = "SPP187.HTM#AO42736"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Information that relates to quantity, technical configuration, type, destination and amount of use of telecommunications service subscribed by customer of telecommunications carrier and made available to carrier by customer solely by virtue of carrier-customer relationship <P>
<A NAME = "AK4277"></A><H3><CENTER>S.652</CENTER>
</H2><P><A NAME = "AK4282"></A><H3>SEC. 703. POLE ATTACHMENTS.
</H3><P><A HREF = "SPP188.HTM#AO428737"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term utility means person being local exchange carrier or electric <P>
<A HREF = "SPP188.HTM#AO428769"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Water, steam or other public utility and owns or controls poles, ducts, conduits or rights-of-way used for wire communications <P>
<A HREF = "SPP188.HTM#AO429318"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term telecommunications carrier not include incumbent local exchange carrier as defined in section <P>
<A HREF = "SPP188.HTM#AO429538"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Access to poles, ducts, conduits and rights-of-way as provided in subsection <P>
<A HREF = "SPP188.HTM#AO43018"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Subsection to apply to rate for pole attachment used by cable television system solely to provide cable service <P>
<A HREF = "SPP188.HTM#AO430157"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Effective date of regulations required under subsection <P>
<A HREF = "SPP188.HTM#AO430180"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Subsection to apply to rate for pole attachment used by cable system or telecommunications carrier to provide telecommunications service <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO430511"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Commission to prescribe regulations in accordance with subsection to govern charges for pole attachments used by telecommunications carriers to provide telecommunications services <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO43077"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>A utility to apportion cost of providing space on pole, duct, conduit or right-of-way other than space among entities <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO430766"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Apportionment equals two-thirds of costs of providing space other than space to be allocated to entity under equal apportionment of costs among attaching entities <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO43097"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>A utility to apportion cost of providing space among entities according to percentage of space required for each entity <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO43118"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Regulations required under paragraph to become effective 5 years after date of enactment of Telecommunications Act of 1996 <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO431173"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Result from adoption of regulations required by subsection to be phased in equal annual increments over period of 5 years beginning on effective date of regulations <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO431310"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>A utility to provide cable television system or telecommunications carrier with nondiscriminatory access to pole <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO431355"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Conduit or right-of-way owned or controlled <P>
<A NAME = "AE15220"></A><A NAME = "AE15220"></A><A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO431516"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Utility providing electric service to deny cable television system or telecommunications carrier access to poles, ducts, conduits or rights-of-way <P>
<A HREF = "SPP189.HTM#AO43177"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>A utility that engages in provision of telecommunications services or cable services to impute to costs of providing services equal amount to pole attachment rate For which company to be liable under section <P>
<A NAME = "AK4321"></A><H3><CENTER>S.652</CENTER>
</H2><P><A NAME = "AK4326"></A><H3>SEC. 704. FACILITIES SITING; RADIO FREQUENCY EMISSION STANDARDS.
</H3><P><A NAME = "AE15260"></A><A HREF = "SPP190.HTM#AO43295"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>NATIONAL WIRELESS TELECOMMUNICATIONS SITING POLICY-Section amended by adding at end following new paragraph <P>
<A HREF = "SPP190.HTM#AO433324"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Nothing in Act to limit or affect authority of State or local government or instrumentality over decisions regarding placement, construction and modification of personal wireless service facilities <P>
<A NAME = "AE15280"></A><A HREF = "SPP190.HTM#AO43437"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>A State or local government or instrumentality to act on request for authorization to place, construct or modify personal wireless service facilities within reasonable period of time after request duly filed with government or instrumentality <P>
<A HREF = "SPP190.HTM#AO43458"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Decision by State or local government or instrumentality to deny request to place, construct or modify personal wireless service facilities in writing and supported by substantial evidence contained in written record <P>
<A NAME = "AE15300"></A><A NAME = "AE15300"></A><A HREF = "SPP190.HTM#AO43476"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>No State or local government or instrumentality to regulate placement, construction and modification of personal wireless service facilities on basis of environmental effects of radio frequency emissions to extent <P>
<A HREF = "SPP190.HTM#AO434783"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Facilities comply with Commission's regulations concerning emissions <P>
<A HREF = "SPP191.HTM#AO43498"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Person adversely affected by final action or failure to act by State or local government or instrumentality being inconsistent with subparagraph to commence action in court of competent jurisdiction <P>
<A HREF = "SPP191.HTM#AO4349129"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Person adversely affected by act or failure to act by State or local government or instrumentality being inconsistent with clause <P>
<A HREF = "SPP191.HTM#AO43578"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term unlicensed wireless service means offering of telecommunications services using duly authorized devices not require individual licenses <P>
<A NAME = "AE15350"></A><A HREF = "SPP191.HTM#AO435934"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Commission to complete action in ET Docket 93-62 to prescribe and make effective rules regarding environmental effects of radio frequency emissions <P>
<A NAME = "AE15360"></A><A NAME = "AE15360"></A><A NAME = "AE15360"></A><A HREF = "SPP191.HTM#AO436132"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>President or designee to prescribe procedures by which Federal departments and agencies to make available on fair, reasonable and nondiscriminatory basis, property, rights-of-way and easements under control for placement of new telecommunications services being dependent in whole or part upon utilization of Federal spectrum rights for transmission or reception of services <P>
<A NAME = "AK4364"></A><H3><CENTER>S.652</CENTER>
</H2><P><A NAME = "AK4369"></A><H3><EM>`PART II--DEVELOPMENT OF COMPETITIVE MARKETS</EM>
</H2><P><A NAME = "AK4372"></A><H3>`SEC. 251. INTERCONNECTION.
</H3><P><A HREF = "SPP192.HTM#AO43756"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>GENERAL DUTY of TELECOMMUNICATIONS CARRIERS-Each telecommunications carrier having duty <P>
<A HREF = "SPP192.HTM#AO437910"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Install network features, functions or capabilities not comply with guidelines and standards established pursuant to section 255 or 256 <P>
<A HREF = "SPP192.HTM#AO43816"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>OBLIGATIONS of LOCAL EXCHANGE CARRIERS-Each local exchange carrier having following duties <P>
<A HREF = "SPP192.HTM#AO438513"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Duty to provide number portability in accordance with requirements prescribed by Commission <P>
<A HREF = "SPP192.HTM#AO438713"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Duty to provide dialing parity to competing providers of telephone exchange service and telephone toll service and duty to permit providers to have nondiscriminatory access to telephone numbers, operator services, directory assistance and directory listing with no unreasonable dialing delays <P>
<A HREF = "SPP193.HTM#AO439341"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Each incumbent local exchange carrier having following duties <P>
<A HREF = "SPP193.HTM#AO439591"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Requesting telecommunications carrier having duty to negotiate in good faith terms and conditions of agreements <P>
<A HREF = "SPP193.HTM#AO440531"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Accordance with terms and conditions of agreement and requirements of section and section 252 <P>
<A HREF = "SPP193.HTM#AO440713"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Duty to provide nondiscriminatory access to network elements on unbundled basis at technically feasible point on rates, terms and conditions being just and nondiscriminatory in accordance with terms and conditions of agreement and requirements of section and section 252 <P>
<A HREF = "SPP193.HTM#AO4407138"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Incumbent local exchange carrier to provide unbundled network elements in manner that allows requesting carriers to combine elements in order to provide telecommunications service <P>
