<A HREF = "SPP194.HTM#AO442392"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Commission determines that subscribers to services denied access to provider of telephone toll services of subscribers' choice and denial being contrary to public interest, convenience and necessity <P>
<A HREF = "SPP194.HTM#AO4423167"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Commission to prescribe regulations to afford subscribers unblocked access to provider of telephone toll services of subscribers' choice through use of carrier identification code assigned to provider or other mechanism <P>
<A HREF = "SPP194.HTM#AO4423244"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Requirements for unblocking not apply to mobile satellite services unless Commission finds in public interest to apply requirements to services <P>
