<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO458356"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Board to determine general policies to govern operations of Fund <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO458387"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Chairman of Board to select, appoint and compensate qualified persons to fill offices <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO4583167"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Prescribed by bylaws or Board of Directors and persons to be officers of Fund and discharge functions, powers and duties <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO458517"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Fund to maintain accounts at financial institution designated for purposes of section by Chairman of Board <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO45876"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Interest transferred pursuant to section of Act <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO45918"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Contributions or donations to Fund accepted by Fund <P>
<A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#AO459327"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Loans, equity or other extensions of credit made from Fund <P>
<A NAME = "AK4597"></A><H3><CENTER>S.652</CENTER>
</H2><P><A NAME = "AK4602"></A><H3>SEC. 708. NATIONAL EDUCATION TECHNOLOGY FUNDING CORPORATION.
</H3><P><A NAME = "AE16270"></A><A HREF = "SPP202.HTM#AO46095"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>CORPORATION There established in District of Columbia private <P>
<A HREF = "SPP202.HTM#AO460935"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Nonprofit corporation known as National Education Technology Funding Corporation being not agency or independent establishment of Federal Government <P>
<A HREF = "SPP202.HTM#AO461114"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Corporation governed by Board of Directors consisting of 15 members <P>
<A NAME = "AE16300"></A><A HREF = "SPP202.HTM#AO46135"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Five members being representative of public agencies representative of schools and public libraries <P>
<A NAME = "AE16310"></A><A NAME = "AE16310"></A><A HREF = "SPP202.HTM#AO46155"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Five members being representative of State government including persons knowledgeable about State finance, technology and education <P>
<A HREF = "SPP202.HTM#AO46175"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Five members being representative of private sector with expertise in network technology, finance and management <P>
<A NAME = "AE16330"></A><A HREF = "SPP202.HTM#AO46217"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>To leverage resources and stimulate private investment in education technology infrastructure <P>
<A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO46295"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Distribute resources to assure equitable aid to elementary schools and secondary schools in State and achieve universal access to network technology <P>
<A NAME = "AE16350"></A><A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO46315"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Upgrade delivery and development of learning through innovative technology-based instructional tools and applications <P>
<A NAME = "AE16360"></A><A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO46337"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>To provide loans, grants and other forms of assistance to State education technology agencies, due regard for providing fair balance among types of school districts and public libraries assisted and disparate needs of districts and libraries <P>
<A NAME = "AE16370"></A><A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO463910"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Purpose of section to recognize Corporation as nonprofit corporation operating under laws of District of Columbia and provide authority for Federal departments and agencies to provide assistance to Corporation <P>
<A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO46437"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term Corporation means National Education Technology Funding Corporation described in subsection <P>
<A NAME = "AE16390"></A><A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO46457"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Terms elementary school and secondary school having same meanings given terms in section 14101 of Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 <P>
<A NAME = "AE16400"></A><A NAME = "AE16400"></A><A NAME = "AE16400"></A><A HREF = "SPP203.HTM#AO46477"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Term public library having same meaning given term in section 3 of Library Services and Construction Act <P>
<A NAME = "AK4651"></A><H3><CENTER>S.652</CENTER>
</H2><P><A NAME = "AK4656"></A><H3>SEC. 709. REPORT ON THE USE OF ADVANCED TELECOMMUNICATIONS SERVICES FOR
MEDICAL PURPOSES.
</H3><P><A NAME = "AE16430"></A><A NAME = "AE16430"></A><A NAME = "AE16430"></A><A NAME = "AE16430"></A><A NAME = "AE16430"></A><A NAME = "AE16430"></A><A NAME = "AE16430"></A><A HREF = "SPP204.HTM#AO46593"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Secretary of Commerce to submit report to Committee on Commerce of House of Representatives and Committee on Commerce, Science and Transportation of Senate concerning activities of Joint Working Group on Telemedicine with findings reached in studies and demonstrations on telemedicine funded by Public Health Service or other Federal agencies <P>
<A HREF = "SPP204.HTM#AO4659172"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Report to examine questions related to patient safety and other legal, medical and economic issues related to utilization of advanced telecommunications services for medical purposes <P>
<A NAME = "AK4661"></A><H3>SEC. 710. AUTHORIZATION OF APPROPRIATIONS.
</H3><P><A HREF = "SPP204.HTM#AO466460"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Necessary to carry out Act and amendments made by Act <P>
<A HREF = "SPP204.HTM#AO466646"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>Additional amounts appropriated pursuant to subsection to be construed to be changes in amounts appropriated for performance of activities described in section of Communications Act of 1934 <P>
<A NAME = "AE16480"></A><A HREF = "SPP204.HTM#AO46685"><img src="LILABS.GIF" ALIGN=MIDDLE></A>FUNDING AVAILABILITY-Section amended by adding at end following new sentence <P>
