<UL><P>`(b) ESTABLISHMENT<A NAME = "AO45246"></A><A NAME = "AS45247"></A><A NAME = "AS45248"></A><A NAME = "AB45249"></A><A HREF = "SPP200.HTM#BB45639"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> OF FUND- There is hereby established a body corporate
