</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(A) 1 shall be eligible to service for a term of 1 year;
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(B) 1 shall be eligible to service for a term of 2 years;
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(C) 1 shall be eligible to service for a term of 3 years;
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(D) 2 shall be eligible to service for a term of 4 years;
and
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><UL><P>`(E) 2 shall be eligible to service for a term of 5 years
(1 of whom shall be the Chairman).
</UL></UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>Directors may continue to serve until their successors have been
appointed and have qualified.
</UL></UL><P>
<UL><UL><P>`(3) MEETINGS AND FUNCTIONS OF THE BOARD- The Board<A NAME = "AO454421"></A><A NAME = "AS454422"></A><A NAME = "AB454423"></A><A HREF = "SPP201.HTM#BB458323"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> of Directors
shall meet at the call of its Chairman, but at least quarterly. 
</UL></UL>
