<title>Concept Page</title>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<A NAME = "AR"></A><A NAME = "AT"></A>

<A HREF = "HOME.HTM#ANC_HP_TOP"><img src="ANCRBAR.GIF" align=middle></A> <strong>Return to Anchor Page</strong>
&#160;&#160;
<A HREF = "SCAP12.HTM#AU"><img src="PREVSEG.GIF" align=middle></A> <strong>Previous</strong>
<hr>
<img src="CONCEPT.GIF" ALIGN =MIDDLE> <strong>CONCEPT VIEW</strong>
<p>
<strong>Choosing an entry on this page will take you to that entry in the full-text document.</strong>
<p>
<DL>
<DT><A HREF = "SPP98.HTM#AS220711">Video system: </A><DD>Prohibit operator of open video system from unreasonably discriminating in favor of operator or affiliates with regard to material or information provided by operator to subscribers for purposes of selecting programming on open video system or way material or information presented to subscribers 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP99.HTM#AS22098">Video system: </A><DD>Require operator of open video system to ensure that video programming providers or copyright holders being able 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP27.HTM#AS6168">Video systems: </A><DD>Establishment of open video systems 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP48.HTM#AS10668">Video systems: </A><DD>Establishment of open video systems 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP72.HTM#AS16148">Video systems: </A><DD>Establishment of open video systems 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP98.HTM#AS22058">Video systems: </A><DD>Extend to distribution of video programming over open video systems Commission's regulations concerning sports exclusivity 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP194.HTM#AS443455">Video telecommunications: </A><DD>Broadband telecommunications capability that enables users to originate and receive high-quality voice, data, graphics and video telecommunications using technology 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP196.HTM#AS446155">Video telecommunications: </A><DD>Broadband telecommunications capability that enables users to originate and receive high-quality voice, data, graphics and video telecommunications using technology 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP107.HTM#AS236446">Visual impairments: </A><DD>Commission to commence inquiry to examine use of video descriptions on video programming in order to ensure accessibility of video programming to persons with visual impairments and report to Congress on findings 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP109.HTM#AS240446">Visual impairments: </A><DD>Commission to commence inquiry to examine use of video descriptions on video programming in order to ensure accessibility of video programming to persons with visual impairments and report to Congress on findings 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP22.HTM#AS48824">Voice mail: </A><DD>Term telemessaging service means voice mail and voice storage and retrieval services 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP22.HTM#AS48823">Voice storage: </A><DD>Term telemessaging service means voice mail and voice storage and retrieval services 
<P><A NAME = "AX147860"></A>&#160;<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP67.HTM#AS147860">Waiver policy: </A><DD>Commission to extend waiver policy to top 50 markets consistent with public interest 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP102.HTM#AS2273171">Waiver request: </A><DD>Commission to grant waiver request within 90 days of application filed under subsection and waiver to be effective for service providers and products in category and providers of services and products 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP104.HTM#AS2303171">Waiver request: </A><DD>Commission to grant waiver request within 90 days of application filed under subsection and waiver to be effective for service providers and products in category and providers of services and products 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP94.HTM#AS21257">Wireline telephone exchange service: </A><DD>Includes successor or assign of company that provides wireline telephone exchange service 
<P><DT><A HREF = "SPP94.HTM#AS2123258">Wisconsin Telephone Company: </A><DD>Pacific Telephone and Telegraph Company or Wisconsin Telephone Company 
<P>
</DL>


