(c), and (d), a telecommunications<A NAME = "AO423134"></A><A NAME = "AS423135"></A><A NAME = "AS423136"></A><A NAME = "BB423137"></A><A HREF = "SPP186.HTM#BB424790"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> carrier that provides telephone<A NAME = "BB423146"></A><A HREF = "SPP187.HTM#BB426746"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> exchange
service shall provide subscriber list information gathered in its capacity
as a provider of such service on a timely and unbundled basis, under
nondiscriminatory and reasonable rates, terms, and conditions, to any person
upon request for the purpose of publishing directories in any format.
</UL><P>
