<H3>SEC. 701. PREVENTION<A NAME = "AS40756"></A><A NAME = "AS40757"></A><A NAME = "AS40758"></A><A NAME = "BB40759"></A><A HREF = "SPP181.HTM#BB41399"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> OF UNFAIR BILLING PRACTICES FOR INFORMATION OR SERVICES<A NAME = "BB407526"></A><A HREF = "SPP181.HTM#BB413926"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A>
