<UL><UL><UL><P>`(C) DEPOSIT AND USE OF AUCTION ESCROW ACCOUNTS- Any deposits<A NAME = "AO444323"></A><A NAME = "AS444324"></A>
the Commission may require for the qualification of any person to bid in
a system of competitive bidding pursuant to this subsection shall be deposited
in an interest bearing account at a financial<A NAME = "AB444391"></A><A HREF = "SPP196.HTM#BB447091"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> institution designated for
