<UL><UL><P>`(8) SUBSCRIPTION<A NAME = "AO41646"></A><A NAME = "AS41647"></A><A NAME = "AS41648"></A><A NAME = "AS41649"></A><A NAME = "BB416410"></A><A HREF = "SPAP2.HTM#AF406110"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> AGREEMENTS FOR BILLING FOR INFORMATION<A NAME = "BB416421"></A><A HREF = "SPAP1.HTM#AF406121"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A> PROVIDED
VIA TOLL<A NAME = "BB416428"></A><A HREF = "SPAP2.HTM#AF406128"><img src="CIRCLINK.GIF"></A>-FREE CALLS-
