<H2>The London Club News</H2>
<H4>Issue 8 -<br>
December 1996</H4>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<H3>In this issue</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#Calls" onMouseOver="self.status=''; return true">Conservative calls</A>
