<HEAD><TITLE>About the London P&amp;I Club</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#BDD0FF" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#400080" ALINK="#004000">
<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=+2>The</FONT> <FONT SIZE=+6>L</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>ondon Steam-Ship Owners' Mutual Insurance Association - </FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>(London P&amp;I Club)</FONT></B>
<P><IMG SRC="images/re_lsso.gif" ALT="Tower Bridge" WIDTH=64 HEIGHT=64 VSPACE=6 ALIGN=right>
<H3>Introduction</H3>

Since 1866, "The London Club" has enabled shipowners to protect themselves against the many legal liabilities to which they are exposed in the course of their business, and against which the ordinary policies on ship, freight, etc., afford no protection.
<P>
Since the London Club was founded, many additional liabilities have been imposed on shipowners, and the cover afforded by the Association has been progressively extended so as to give shipowners the protection which experience has shown to be most required. The terms of the present comprehensive insurance are contained in the Association's Rules, copies of which can be obtained from the Managers, (see <A HREF="contact.htm" onMouseOver="self.status='Contact info for the Managers and correspondents worldwide'; return true">Contacting the Club</A>) but the particulars given in this website's <A HREF="re_p_i.htm" onMouseOver="self.status='About the insurance cover offered by the London Club'; return true"> "About P&amp;I"</A> page will indicate the main features of the cover. 
<P>
<A HREF="#Committee" onMouseOver="self.status='The shipowners comprising the London Club Committee'; return true">The Committee,</A> which consists of shipowners, meets frequently, thus ensuring prompt attention to claims.
<P>
The Managers at <A HREF="re_abc.htm" onMouseOver="self.status='About A Bilbrough &amp; Co Ltd'; return true"> A Bilbrough &amp; Co Ltd</A> draw on a range of skills, with expertise in law, insurance, accountancy and seamanship. 
<P>
Further, the Association maintains correspondents at over 300 ports throughout the world who are available to assist Members and their Masters in case of need. An up-to-date list of <A HREF="contact.htm#Correspondents" onMouseOver="self.status='Contact details for correspondents, sorted geographically';return true">correspondents' contact details</A> is available on this site.
<P>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
