<HEAD><TITLE>London P&amp;I Club News</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFE0" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#400080" ALINK="#004000">

<B><FONT SIZE=+2>The</FONT> <FONT SIZE=+6>L</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>ondon Steam-Ship Owners' Mutual Insurance Association - </FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>Newsletters</FONT></B>
<P><IMG SRC="images/newslets.gif" ALT="Newsletters" WIDTH=64 HEIGHT=64 VSPACE=6 ALIGN=RIGHT>
<H3><FONT FACE="Arial", "Helvetica">The London Club News<BR>
The StopLoss Bulletin</FONT></H3>
<P>
<A HREF="#LCN" onMouseOver="self.status='London Club News - Index';return true"><IMG SRC="lcn/images/lcn_logo.gif" ALT="LCN logo" WIDTH=202 HEIGHT=58 BORDER="0" HSPACE=8 ALIGN=left></A>The London Club News is published bi-monthly, with updates and information about the Club, its Managers at A Bilbrough &amp; Co, and news and current events from the worlds of shipping, marine insurance and loss prevention.
<P>
<A HREF="#SLB" onMouseOver="self.status='London Club StopLoss Bulletins - Index';return true"><IMG SRC="slb/images/slb_logo.gif" ALT="StopLoss logo" WIDTH=203 HEIGHT=68 HSPACE=8 BORDER="0" ALIGN=left></A>The StopLoss Bulletin, published quarterly, focuses more closely on loss prevention, mixing brief case studies from which ship managers can draw salutory lessons, with practical advice for the avoidance of some of the many hazards - physical, legal, environmental and financial - faced by the shipping community.
<P>
<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center SIZE=2>
<A NAME="Index"></A>
<FONT COLOR="#FFFFE0">.</FONT><br>
These publications are circulated to our Members and Correspondents in paper form, but all are available from this site.
<P>
<B>The next publication will be the January 1997 StopLoss Bulletin.</B>
<P>
<HR WIDTH=80% ALIGN=center SIZE=2>
<BR> 
<BR>
<A NAME="LCN">
<FONT COLOR="#FFFFE0">.</FONT><br>
