<HEAD><TITLE>Contact the London Club</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<A NAME="Top"></A><BODY BGCOLOR="#A4C8F0" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#400080" ALINK="#004000"><BASEFONT SIZE=3>

<B><FONT SIZE=+2>The</FONT> <FONT SIZE=+6>L</FONT><FONT SIZE=+2>ondon Steam-Ship Owners' Mutual Insurance Association - </FONT><FONT SIZE=+1>Contacting the Club</FONT></B>
<P><IMG SRC="images/contact.gif" ALT="Contact AB&amp;Co" WIDTH=64 HEIGHT=64 VSPACE=6 ALIGN=right>
The Managers of the Club, A Bilbrough &amp; Co, have earned a reputation for the highest quality of service to Members. Part of this is accessibility - a quick response and efficient handling of queries, particularly in relation to claims or legal matters. 
<P>
Representatives of A Bilbrough &amp; Co can be contacted in a number of ways:
<BR>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#London" onMouseOver="self.status='50 Leman Street, London E1 8HQ'; return true">London Office</A>
<LI><A HREF="#Hong Kong" onMouseOver="self.status='1505 Guardian House, 32 Oi Kwan Road'; return true">Hong Kong Office</A> <BR>
<LI><A HREF="#Piraeus" onMouseOver="self.status='67 Akti Miaouli, 185 37 Piraeus'; return true">Piraeus Office</A>
<BR>
<LI>Correspondents around the world:<BR>
-	<A HREF="#Correspondents" onMouseOver="self.status='Select area from a world map, then by country'; return true">Map</A> of the world<BR>
-	<A HREF="#List" onMouseOver="self.status='Select the country of interest from a list';return true">List</A> of countries, sorted by regions<BR>
</UL>
<A NAME="E-mail form"></A><H4>Contact us by e-mail</H4>
You can also send an e-mail message to the London Office (which will be forwarded to the appropriate person at A Bilbrough &amp; Co wherever they are based) using this pre-addressed <A HREF="mailto:webmail@a-bilbrough.co.uk" onMouseOver="self.status='Send an e-mail message to A Bilbrough &amp; Co';return true">form</A>. 
<P>
<FONT  SIZE=-1><EM>
<LI>Please note that e-mail should not be used for sensitive or confidential messages, and that transmission over the internet can involve delays.
<P>
<LI>Please do <STRONG>not</STRONG> send new claims notifications solely by e-mail, as we cannot guarantee that they will arrive expeditiously at A Bilbrough & Co.
<P>
</EM></FONT>
