<BR>
<H3>Correspondents</H3>

Each red dot on this map represents a port or city where the services of a Correspondent are retained, to whom reference can be made in matters which might involve the Association's cover. 
<P>
Correspondents can act on a Member's behalf to protect his interests, but Members are reminded that at the same time they should notify the Managers.
