<HEAD>
<META Name="description" Content="Home page for the London P&I Club, a leading member of the International Group of P&I Clubs, third-party liability insurers for the vast majority of the world's shipping">
<META Name="keywords" Content="London P&I Club, LSSO, Mutual Insurance, Marine, Maritime, Third Party, Protection, Indemnity, Freight, Demurrage, Defence, Defense, FDD, FD&D, London Steam-Ship Owners' Mutual Insurance Association, Ship, Shipping, Bilbrough, Leman">
<TITLE>The London P&amp;I Club</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<FRAMESET COLS="114,*">

<BASEFONT SIZE=3>
<NOFRAMES>
<BR>
<IMG SRC="images/anilogo1.gif" WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60 ALIGN=LEFT>
<P>
<STRONG>The London Steam-Ship Owners'<BR>
Mutual Insurance Association Limited</STRONG>
<P>
<BR>
<BR>
Welcome to <STRONG>www.lsso.com,</STRONG> the London P&amp;I Club's web site. The London Club is one of the leading members of the International Group of Protection and Indemnity Associations (P&amp;I Clubs), which together insure the vast majority of the world's merchant shipping against third-party risks.
<P>
This site has been enhanced to work best using <STRONG>Netscape Navigator 3</STRONG> browser software.
<P>
If you have a different browser, you may experience some difficulties with the site. As a test, unless you can load the little logo above and after a few seconds it performs a brief animation, you should consider upgrading. 
<P>
However, by entering <STRONG><A HREF="home.htm">here</A></STRONG>, you can have access to all the information, although the site may not be presented properly and some features may not work. Alternatively, Netscape's latest browser software is available for downloading from <A HREF="http://home.netscape.com">Netscape's Home Page</A>.
<P>
<BR>
