<title>Participants in 1991 G-7 Economic Summit   
Meeting</title><body><HTML> 
<B><h4><img align=left src="g7logo.gif" alt=G-7 Logo>
<center>The United States at the G-7</h4></B>
<H3>  1991: London Economic Summit, July 15 - 17            
<hr></H3></center>


Participants at the 2-day meeting:<P>  
<UL>
<LI>President George Bush of the United States of America  
<LI>Prime Minister John Major of the United Kingdom  
<LI>President Francois Mitterand of the Republic of France  
<LI>Chancellor Helmut Kohl of the Federal Republic of Germany  
<LI>Prime Minister Brian Mulroney of Canada  
<LI>Prime Minister Toshiki Kaifu of Japan  
<LI>Prime Minister Giulio Andreotti of Italy  
<LI>President Jacques Delors of the European Community Commission

<p>  
<li><A HREF="1991note.htm">Notes from the Summit</A>
<li><A HREF="1992.htm">Next year's file</A>
<p>  
</UL>
