http://gopher.usia.gov:80/topical/econ/wto/sing1209.htm 198.80.36.82 19970213141924 text/html 12989
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thu, 13 Feb 1997 14:19:09 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
Content-type: text/html
